data.description: This magnificent home is designed to captivate and impress at every turn. Gaze at majestic mountains and city lights from your saltwater pool while preparing family meals in your new outdoor kitchen. The soaring celling includes expansive windows offering tons of natural light. Be dazzled with the fine finishings and extraordinary upgrades. The chef's kitchen has a well-appointed bar and wine cooler perfect for entertaining. Large bedroom and full bathroom downstairs for added privacy. Perched high in the hills of Lake Las Vegas, home to 2 championship Jack Nicklaus Signature Golf Courses, fine dining, shopping, water sports and more! $12,000 Sports Club Initiation Fee waived. Welcome home!
